{"tid":2096601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人今個星期得一個任務 就係準備好初選","createTime":"2020-07-06T08:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:40:44.000Z","uid":126153,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"572189b6fc032af07b9166b728dc6adfaae27e17","tid":2096601,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"成個熱門得一個post講緊<br />\n大家關心渣哥抽水仲多過初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係唔係唔撚記得左上次公投有幾撚失敗？</span></span><br />\n今次歷史性初選係要準備更多野<br />\n要down app要scan code<br />\n<br />\n初選投票流程+注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2096501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2096501</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好比我睇死 <br />\n到時肯定有一堆港豬寧願去沙灘都唔投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得體制內抗爭無用 初選有鳩佢<br />\n咁我想同你講<br />\n有好撚多野未做之前都係覺得無撚用<br />\n當年打國際線 好多人都話要靠自己 唔靠外國<br />\n有邊個估到今日bno平權可以觸動到共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到依家靠自己搞到初選<br />\n我唔該你地尊重下人地既effort<br />\n禁幾個制 睇幾行字都懶 唔好同我講光復香港<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個唔投初選 我一定屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6aab0994bc4903240d70e84c17d3d39f78bf4df","tid":2096601,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"01b47e83d680855a189a48ab33015d9402ce701f","tid":2096601,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c23a3b3538995e60b550628afa625909fed19f87","tid":2096601,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a01d81025d1fbd999bbf70ca9d4c0ad59f6b6eac","tid":2096601,"uid":126153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c78d26f06dc00a1d020f3bb06f7c748b0653bca8","tid":209660